                            <comment id="16515767" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 18 Jun 2018 14:22:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1833727 from tilman@apache.org in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1833727&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1833727&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

