                            <comment id="16515774" author="tilman" created="Mon, 18 Jun 2018 14:24:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Revert because of regressions. Sorry, this didn&apos;t appear the last times I ran the tests. &lt;del&gt;I found out that the files were missing on one of my computers.&lt;/del&gt; I don&apos;t know what happened. The files are there. Maybe I had done too much editing back and forth or on different project files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The regression is about transparency groups in a rotated page.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16552140" author="pslabycz" created="Sun, 22 Jul 2018 20:14:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt;: Could you please link or attach the files which had the regression so that we could have a look? We cannot use PDFBox 2.0 in our product until this issue is resolved.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16552142" author="tilman" created="Sun, 22 Jul 2018 20:21:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;But I did. It&apos;s the gs-bugzilla690022 files that are attached to this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16552145" author="pslabycz" created="Sun, 22 Jul 2018 20:25:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ooops, sorry. Thx.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16555731" author="kunhart" created="Wed, 25 Jul 2018 14:08:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt;: We have made the new patch &quot;pdfbox-2.0.10-SNAPSHOT_transparency_group_sources_2.patch&quot;, which help us to use the PDFBox 2.0 and it doesn&apos;t break the tests here. The change is simple, we only allow to override the method PageDrawer#adjustRectangle() and adjust there the translations of the softmask if someone need some. We have also updated the test example &quot;TestPDFToImage&quot;, where is overriden method already used and it works well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16555996" author="tilman" created="Wed, 25 Jul 2018 17:16:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is that if we make this public, it becomes part of the API and we can&apos;t remove it. The comment above that method you want to make public shows that it is not stable at all.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My impression in June was that some part of your patch would have to be modified to take care of the rotation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16574705" author="kunhart" created="Thu, 9 Aug 2018 11:18:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; I have attached the patches for pdfbox-2.0.12 and pdfbox-3.0.0, where I hope is definitely solved this issue and it works well with our examples and also with your attached pdf from your tests. Please try it. Thx.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16577122" author="jira-bot" created="Sat, 11 Aug 2018 10:20:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1837852 from tilman@apache.org in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1837852&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1837852&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4245&quot; title=&quot;wrong rendering of the transparency group at the specific position on a page&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-4245&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-4245&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: fix bug and simplify code that adjusts for rotations so that initial translation doesn&apos;t get lost, by Jiri Kunhart&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16577123" author="jira-bot" created="Sat, 11 Aug 2018 10:20:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1837853 from tilman@apache.org in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1837853&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1837853&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

